query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `drug_interaction_checks` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `user_id` int NOT NULL,
  `performed_by` int NOT NULL,
  `medications_checked` text NOT NULL,
  `conditions_considered` text,
  `interactions_found` int DEFAULT 0,
  `highest_severity` enum('none','minor','moderate','major','contraindicated') DEFAULT 'none',
  `overall_risk` enum('low','moderate','high') DEFAULT 'low',
  `full_results` text,
  `notes` text,
  `created_at` timestamp DEFAULT (now()),
  CONSTRAINT `drug_interaction_checks_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
)
